'''雅克‧法斯科'''（'''Jacque Fresco'''，{{bd|1916年|3月13日|2017年|5月18日|catIdx=Fresco}})， 是自學成才的建築設計師、社會工程师、工業設計師、作家、演說家、發明家和一名未來主義者，他透過他創辦的[[維納斯計劃|維納斯計劃]]，以及[[時代精神運動|時代精神運動]]等積極分享他關於社會結構的遠大構想和相關可行措施，也稱自己為一名未來主義者。他精力過人，好奇心旺盛，不停發現並解決問題，和許多發明家和科學家就跨領域合作。

法斯科著力於撰寫、演講，發表他在諸如[[生態城市|生態城市]]、能源使用效率、自然資源管理、[[模控學|模控科技]]、[[自動化|自動化]]、科技在社會中的地位等等的看法。他主導[[維納斯計劃|維納斯計劃]]<ref name="The Venus Project Inc.">{{citation |title=The Venus Project Inc. |publisher=Florida Department of State Division of Corporations |url=http://search.sunbiz.org/Inquiry/CorporationSearch/SearchResultDetail/EntityName/domnp-n94000000493-3467f9d7-a3a9-440c-9568-0e060272ffd1/The%20Venus%20Project/Page1 |accessdate=2013-05-28 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220005158/http://search.sunbiz.org/Inquiry/CorporationSearch/SearchResultDetail/EntityName/domnp-n94000000493-3467f9d7-a3a9-440c-9568-0e060272ffd1/The%20Venus%20Project/Page1 |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，並提倡全球性貫徹實施一種特別的社會經濟系統，他稱之為「[[資源導向型經濟|資源導向型經濟]]」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fzirIG55fkE |title=TEDxOjai - Jacque Fresco - Resource Based Economy |publisher=YouTube |date= |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106073300/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fzirIG55fkE |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-23799590 |title=BBC News - Tomorrow's cities: How the Venus Project is redesigning the future |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2013-08-26 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512020047/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-23799590 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 早年生涯 ==

雅克‧法斯科生於1916年3月13日<ref name="1930 Census">{{Citation | title = 1930 Census | medium = Original Document | publisher = U.S. Department of Commerce | location = Brooklyn, New York | date = April 3, 1930 | url = http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:1930_-_Federal_Census_-_Brooklyn_%28document%29.jpg | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2021-03-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210331102153/https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:1930_-_Federal_Census_-_Brooklyn_(document).jpg | dead-url = no }}</ref>，紐約布魯克林本森赫斯特<ref>{{cite web |last=Gore |first=Jeff |url=http://orlandoweekly.com/news/the-view-from-venus-1.1217175?pgno=4 |title=The view from Venus - News & Features |publisher=Orlando Weekly |date=2011-10-13 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009201800/http://orlandoweekly.com/news/the-view-from-venus-1.1217175?pgno=4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一個塞法迪猶太家庭中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tabletmag.com/jewish-news-and-politics/57732/brave-new-world |title=Brave New World |publisher=''[[Tablet_Magazine|Tablet Magazine]]'' |accessdate=2013-10-13 |archive-date=2017-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111015859/http://www.tabletmag.com/jewish-news-and-politics/57732/brave-new-world |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。西元1929年，美國爆發[[大蕭條|大蕭條]]時正值其青少年時期。他曾花時間與朋友討論有關[[達爾文|達爾文]]、[[愛因斯坦|愛因斯坦]]、當時的[[科學|科學]]和所面臨的[[未來|未來]]。<ref name="Rolfe 168, 169, 170">{{Citation | last = Rolfe | first = Lionel | title = Fat Man on the Left | place = Los Angeles | publisher = California Classics Books | year = 1998 | chapter = Unpopular Science | pages = 166–170 | isbn = 978-1-879395-01-5 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=lSX9pwnsOc4C&lpg=PP1&dq=fat%20man%20on%20the%20left&pg=PA168#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2014-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140618021236/http://books.google.com/books?id=lSX9pwnsOc4C&lpg=PP1&dq=fat%20man%20on%20the%20left&pg=PA168#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>他同時也參加了青年共產國際美國分支(Young Communist League USA)，經過與其主席會面和討論後，法斯科大聲表示「[[馬克思|馬克思]]錯了！」並憤然離去。<ref name="Rolfe 158-161">{{Citation | last = Rolfe | first = Lionel | title = Fat Man on the Left | place = Los Angeles | publisher = California Classics Books | year = 1998 | chapter = Unpopular Science | pages = 158–161 | isbn = 978-1-879395-01-5 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=lSX9pwnsOc4C&lpg=PP1&dq=fat%20man%20on%20the%20left&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2013-12-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131229083113/http://books.google.com/books?id=lSX9pwnsOc4C&lpg=PP1&dq=fat%20man%20on%20the%20left&pg=PP1#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>之後，他把注意力轉向了[[專家統治|專家統治]]。<ref name="Rolfe 168, 169, 170"/>

== 工作生涯 ==

=== 航空工業 ===

1930年代後期，法斯科在[[加州|加州]]的[[道格拉斯飛行器公司|道格拉斯飛行器公司]]工作。<ref name="Rolfe 158-161"/><ref name="Smith 2">{{Cite news | last = Smith | first = Mac. | title = A Look Ahead Through Fresco's Window | newspaper = Florida Living Magazine | location = Miami | pages = 2–3 | date = December 31, 1961 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OAxgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=UOkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1604%2C4941153 | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2013-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130909031143/http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OAxgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=UOkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1604%2C4941153 | dead-url = no }}</ref>當時他提出了一些設計，包括機翼<ref>I. {{Citation | last = | first = | title = Flying Wing | journal = Great Lakes Technocrat. | volume = Vol. 11, No. 11, July–Aug. 1944 | page = 34}}</ref>以及碟型飛機。某些設計在當時被認為不切實際，因此他的想法並未被採用。<ref name="Rejected">{{Cite news | last = Andreeva | first = Tamara. | title = Advanced Plane Ideas Rejected | newspaper = [[Abilene_Reporter-News|Abilene Reporter-News]] | location = Abilene, TX | page = 9 | date = March 6, 1950 | url =}}</ref>之後，因為設計理念不合，法斯科辭去了在道格拉斯的工作。<ref name="Rolfe 158-161"/><ref name="Rejected"/>

1942年，法斯科被編入美國軍隊。<ref name="Rolfe 168, 169, 170"/><ref name="Jacque Army">{{cite web |url=http://aad.archives.gov/aad/record-detail.jsp?dt=893&mtch=1&tf=F&q=39532348&bc=&rpp=10&pg=1&rid=7956301 |title=NARA - AAD - Display Full Records - Electronic Army Serial Number Merged File, ca. 1938 - 1946 (Enlistment Records) |publisher=Aad.archives.gov |date= |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325092019/https://aad.archives.gov/aad/record-detail.jsp?dt=893&mtch=1&tf=F&q=39532348&bc=&rpp=10&pg=1&rid=7956301 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
他被分配到[[美國陸軍航空軍|美國陸軍航空軍]]在[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[代頓|代頓]][[萊特廣場|萊特廣場]]設計實驗室從事技術設計的工作。<ref name="Rolfe 168, 169, 170"/><ref name="Scully">{{Citation | last = Scully | first = Frank | title = Behind the Flying Saucers | place = New York | publisher = Henry Holt & Co. | year =1950 | chapter = The Aerodynamic Correction | pages = 122–123}}</ref><ref name="Rejected"/><ref name="Trip Moon">{{Cite news| title = A Trip to the Moon| newspaper = [[The_Miami_Herald|The Miami Herald]] Sunday Magazine| location = Miami| pages = Section G| date = April 8, 1956| url = http://www.thevenusproject.com/images/stories/archived-media/Newspapers/1956%20-%20MiamiHerald/Binder1.pdf| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130827075657/http://www.thevenusproject.com/images/stories/archived-media/Newspapers/1956%20-%20MiamiHerald/Binder1.pdf| archivedate =2013-08-27}}</ref>當時他設計了一種特別的機翼，稱之為「根部可變式弧形翼」，試圖透過允許飛行員在起飛和飛行過程中調節機翼厚度以使飛行控制最佳化。<ref>{{Citation | title = Wing Changes Its Camber | journal = [[Popular_Science|Popular Science]]. | volume = Vol. 150, No. 5 | page = 115 | date = May 1947 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=KiYDAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA115&dq=jacque%20fresco%20popular%20science&pg=PA115#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2014-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140620114928/http://books.google.com/books?id=KiYDAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA115&dq=jacque%20fresco%20popular%20science&pg=PA115#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation | title = Hydraulic Jack to Alter Airplane Wing's Camber | journal = [[Science_News|Science News]] Letter. | volume = Vol. 50, No. 20 | page = 310 | date = November 16, 1946 | jstor = 3923108}}</ref> 但最終，他因為不適應軍隊模式而離去。<ref name="Rolfe 168, 169, 170"/>



=== 新潮之家 ===

法斯科接受了蒙茨（{{link-en||Madman Muntz}}）的委託，幫他設計成本更低的房屋。他與Harry Giaretto、Eli Catran兩位同夥一同構思、設計和建造之。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.scribd.com/doc/68209417/003-1948-06-XX-Official-Trend-Home-Brochure |title=[003] - 1948.06.XX - Official Trend Home Brochure |publisher=Scribd.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306151703/https://www.scribd.com/doc/68209417/003-1948-06-XX-Official-Trend-Home-Brochure |dead-url=no }}</ref>整個計劃於1948年夏天開展，<ref name="Orlando">{{cite web |last=Gore |first=Jeff |url=http://orlandoweekly.com/news/the-view-from-venus-1.1217175 |title=The view from Venus - News & Features |publisher=Orlando Weekly |date=2011-10-13 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009191702/http://orlandoweekly.com/news/the-view-from-venus-1.1217175 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而當時32歲的法斯科完成了他傳統職業生涯中最為成功的作品「新潮之家」。作為[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]在[[好萊塢|好萊塢]][[日落大道|日落大道]]第8舞台的重點展示，「新潮之家」幾乎僅由鋁材和玻璃所構成。在三個月展期內前往該處參觀的花費僅需一美元。<ref name="Orlando"/>展示收益全數捐給了[[癌症預防協會|癌症預防協會]]。之後，「新潮之家」計劃需要聯邦基金資助，但遭到了拒絕。

=== 科學研究實驗室 ===

在1940年代後期，法斯科在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]創立了科學研究實驗室並主導之。<ref name="Trip Moon"/><ref name="Scientific Research Laboratories">{{cite web |url=http://kepler.sos.ca.gov/cbs.aspx |title=Business Search - Business Entities - Business Programs |publisher=Kepler.sos.ca.gov |date= |accessdate=2014-06-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100402014221/http://kepler.sos.ca.gov/cbs.aspx |archivedate=2010-04-02 }}</ref>在此處，他舉辦演講，同時也傳授技術設計<ref name="Rolfe 158-161"/>，作為自由研究者和科學顧問，他同時展開研究、工作和發明。<ref>{{Citation | title = Plastics with a Charge Have Magical Effects | journal = [[Popular_Mechanics|Popular Mechanics]]. | volume = 'Vol. 104, No. 6 | page = 149 | date = Dec 1955 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=wt0DAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA149&dq=jacque%20fresco%20popular%20mechanics&pg=PA149#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2014-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140121113602/http://books.google.com/books?id=wt0DAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA149&dq=jacque%20fresco%20popular%20mechanics&pg=PA149#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>
在此期間，法斯科努力爭取其研究資助<ref name="Frustrated">{{Cite news | last = Andreeva | first = Tamara. | title = Frustrated Genius | newspaper = [[Olean_Times_Herald|Olean Times Herald]] | location = New York | page = 13 | date = March 3, 1950 | url = http://access.newspaperarchive.com.ezproxy.lapl.org/Viewer.aspx?img=35636251&firstvisit=true&src=search&currentResult=3&currentPage=0&fpo=False}}</ref>，也面臨挫敗和財務上的困難。1955年，由於[[5號州際公路加利福尼亞州段|5號州際公路加利福尼亞州段]]工程之故，法斯科的研究室最終被拆除，而他也離開了加州。<ref name="Rolfe 158-161"/><ref name="Smith 2"/>

== 中年生涯 ==

1955年，法斯科搬到了[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]的[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]。他開了一家提供心理諮詢的公司，但他在這方面並沒有受過正式課程訓練。<ref name="Smith 2"/>在收到了來自[[美國心理學協會|美國心理學協會]]一連串「批評攻勢」之後，法斯科終止了該業務。<ref name="Smith 2"/>從該段時間內的報紙文章指出法斯科當時聲稱自己擁有來自加州洛杉磯[[拉西瑞亞大學|拉西瑞亞大學]]的正式學位，但未經證實。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thevenusproject.com/images/stories/archived-media/Newspapers/1956%20-%20MiamiHerald/Binder1.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-03-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827075657/http://www.thevenusproject.com/images/stories/archived-media/Newspapers/1956%20-%20MiamiHerald/Binder1.pdf |archivedate=2013-08-27 }}</ref>

法斯科描述了他之前所加入的團體和組織，例如他面對過白人至上主義者並測試改變他們的可能性。他講述之前加入[[3K黨|3K黨]]和[[白人公民委員會|白人公民委員會]]的過程，以及試圖改變他們對於種族歧視看法的經過。<ref name="TVPmag">{{cite web |url= http://www.tvpmagazine.com/2012/01/the-immaculate-pig-experiment-by-jacque-fresco/ |title= The Immaculate Pig Experiment |last1= Fresco |first1= Jacque |date= January 28, 2012 |publisher= TVP Magazine |accessdate= March 18, 2012 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120306181818/http://www.tvpmagazine.com/2012/01/the-immaculate-pig-experiment-by-jacque-fresco/ |archivedate=2012-03-06}}</ref>

在[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]，法斯科發表了他的圓形城市設計。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.co.cr/floating-cities-and-resource-based-economies/2954/ |title=Floating Cities and Resource-Based Economies |publisher=News.co.cr |date=2012-02-27 |accessdate=2014-06-25 |archive-date=2017-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703125145/http://news.co.cr/floating-cities-and-resource-based-economies/2954/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在美國鋁業公司和專業地產公司等企業中，法斯科以一名工業設計師的身分活躍著。<ref name="Smith 2"/>

1961年，Pietro Belluschi（{{link-en||Pietro Belluschi}}）和C. Frederick Wise<ref name="House">{{Cite news | last = | first = | title = $2,950 House Shell Made of Aluminum | newspaper = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | location = New York | pages = 1R, 8R | date = May 28, 1961}}</ref> 與法斯科共同在一項計劃上合作，名為「Sandwich House」。<ref name="Smith 2"/>包括大部分的預置組件、隔間和鋁材在內，它售價2,950美元。或者，也可額外選購所有內部基本設施，價位為7,500美元。<ref name="House"/>在此期間，法斯科透過他的雅克法斯科公司預先製造鋁材以支持其計劃。<ref>I. {{Citation | title = We've Changed The Rules | journal = [[Popular_Science|Popular Science]]. | volume = Vol. 190, No. 3 | page = 215 | date = March 1967 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=4yADAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA215&dq=jacque%20fresco%20science&pg=PA215#v=onepage&q&f=false | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2014-06-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140621160540/http://books.google.com/books?id=4yADAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA215&dq=jacque%20fresco%20science&pg=PA215#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url = no }}
* II. {{Citation | title = Rack 'Em Up | journal = American Artist. | volume = Vol. 31, No. 3 | page = 8 | date = March 1967 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=CVQ9AAAAMAAJ | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2013-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130909034555/http://books.google.com/books?id=CVQ9AAAAMAAJ | dead-url = no }}
* III. {{Citation | title = Pamper Your Pipes | journal = [[Esquire_(magazine)|Esquire]]. | volume = | page = 163 | date = March 1967}}
* IV. {{citation |title=Jacque Fresco Enterprises Inc. |publisher=Florida Department of State Division of Corporations |url=http://search.sunbiz.org/Inquiry/CorporationSearch/SearchResultDetail/EntityName/domp-307282-5bb6b9fc-5cf5-4950-bba7-215fcb624850/Jacque%20Fresco%20Enterprises%20Inc/Page1 |accessdate=2013-05-28 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128092604/http://search.sunbiz.org/Inquiry/CorporationSearch/SearchResultDetail/EntityName/domp-307282-5bb6b9fc-5cf5-4950-bba7-215fcb624850/Jacque%20Fresco%20Enterprises%20Inc/Page1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1955至1969年間，法斯科稱其社會構想為「美洲計劃」。

=== 「展望未來」 ===

1969年，《展望未來》（''Looking Forward''）正式出版。該書由[[Ken_Keyes,_Jr.|Ken Keyes Jr.]]和法斯科合著。 《展望未來》是一本對於未來推測性的窺探的書籍。作者們描繪了這樣一個想法：建立一個科技高度控制化的社會，不再有任何匱乏產生，工作和私人財產也將不復存在；這個社會將聚焦並著力於滿足每個人的需求。<ref name="Lib Journ 1971">{{Citation | last = Cross | first = Michael S. | title = Review: 'Looking Forward' | journal = [[Library_Journal|Library Journal]]. | volume = Vol. 94| year= 1970 | page = 612}}</ref>

=== 「Sociocyberneering」 ===

