* II. {{Cite news | last = Bassett | first = Melanie. | title = Man Need Not Fear Machine | newspaper = The Carolinian | location = Raleigh, NC | page = 4 | date = March 6, 1970 | url = }}
* III. {{Cite news | last = | first = | title = Series to Explore Suicide or Survival | newspaper = [[Tampa_Bay_Times|St. Petersburg Times]] | location = St. Petersburg, FL | pages = 3B | date = April 23, 1970 | url = }}
* IV. {{Cite news | last = Steigleman | first = Walt. | title = 'Jules Vernesque' City Shows Plans at USF | newspaper = [[The_Oracle_(University_of_South_Florida)|The Oracle]] | location = Tampa, FL | page = 9 | date = October 20, 1971 | url = }}</ref>和電視、廣播節目等方式推廣他的組織。<ref name="King">{{Cite video | people = The Larry King Show | title = Larry King Interview | medium = Television | publisher = WTVJ 4 | location = Miami | date = August 19, 1974 | url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PN6puH9DYnQ | access-date = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2021-02-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210202214041/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PN6puH9DYnQ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Montage">{{Cite video | people = Renick, Ralph; Abrell, Joe; Fresco, Jacque | title = Montage Interview | medium = Television | publisher = Montage (WTVJ) | date = January 26, 1974 | url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=th7ogCI4oP4 | access-date = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2017-11-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171120100319/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=th7ogCI4oP4 | dead-url = no }}</ref>之後，法斯科的「sociocyberneering」會員群體並未繼續發展，而是在[[佛羅里達|佛羅里達]]的[[維納斯_(地名)|維納斯]]購置了一片土地。他遷居至該地，並將他的研究中心也一併設置於此。<ref>{{Cite news | last = Tice | first = Neysa. | title = Venus Is Headquarters For Sociocyberneering Research Center | newspaper = Lake Placid Journal | location = Lake Placid, FL | pages = 1B | date = October 29, 1981 | url = http://www.thevenusproject.com/images/stories/archived-media/Newspapers/1981%20-%20LakePlacidJournal/Binder1.pdf | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130827080616/http://www.thevenusproject.com/images/stories/archived-media/Newspapers/1981%20-%20LakePlacidJournal/Binder1.pdf | archivedate =2013-08-27}}</ref>

== 維納斯計劃和近年工作 ==

1994年，法斯科開啟了[[維納斯計劃|維納斯計劃]]。<ref name="The Venus Project Inc."/>



整個1990年代，法斯科與羅克珊‧梅多斯透過自由職業者的發明<ref>{{Cite news | last = Eyman | first = Scott. | title = The Great Idea Chase | newspaper = [[Sun-Sentinel|Sun-Sentinel]] | location = Fort Lauderdale, FL | page = 7 date = July 14, 1985 | url = http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1985-07-14/features/8501280616_1_inventors-idea-garage | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2012-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120826004641/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1985-07-14/features/8501280616_1_inventors-idea-garage | dead-url = no }}</ref>、工業工程、傳統建築建模<ref name="Orlando Weekly">{{Cite news | last = Gore | first = Jeff. | title = The View from Venus | newspaper = [[Orlando_Weekly|Orlando Weekly]] | location = Orlando, FL | pages =  | date = October 13, 2011 | url = http://orlandoweekly.com/news/the-view-from-venus-1.1217175 | accessdate = 2015-01-26 | archive-date = 2014-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009191702/http://orlandoweekly.com/news/the-view-from-venus-1.1217175 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 和發明協商<ref name="Orlando Weekly"/>來支撐計劃的運作。

2002年，法斯科出版了他的主要工作成果《用錢買不到的美好事物》（''The Best That Money Can't Buy''）。2006年，知名導演威廉·加薩基（{{link-en||William Gazecki}}）執導了敘述法斯科的半自傳式電影《設計‧未來》（{{lang|en|Future by Design}}）"<ref name="Future By Design">Gazecki, W. (2006). {{YouTube|Xxe7tlr-2I4|''Future by Design.''}} Docflix.</ref>2008年，[[彼得‧約瑟夫|彼得‧約瑟夫]]（{{link-en||Peter Joseph}}）以法斯科為主角，執導了《時代精神：附錄》，將其對於未來的願景化作具體可行的替代方案。[[彼得‧約瑟夫|彼得‧約瑟夫]]，[[時代精神運動|時代精神運動]]的創始人開始倡導法斯科的方法。但在2012年4月，由於對目的和目標產生分歧，兩個團體宣告分道揚鑣。<ref name="Orlando Weekly"/>

在2012年4月，羅克珊梅多斯發布了電影，天堂或遺忘，總結了目標和維納斯計劃的建議。在2012年6月，瑪雅博格放映她的影片，未來我的愛，在愛丁堡國際電影節為特色法斯科和羅克珊梅多斯的工作。
目前，法斯科保存講座和參觀的維納斯計劃位置。

2010年間，人在美國的法斯科試圖對「資源導向型經濟」申請商標<ref>[http://tmportal.uspto.gov/external/portal/tow?SRCH=Y&isSubmitted=true&details=&SELECT=US+Serial+No&TEXT=77829193# Resource Based Economy Trademark], United States Patent & Trademark Office</ref> 並進行了審查，但該詞過於通稱化，因此商標的申請遭到當局拒絕。

西元2010年整年間，法斯科與梅多斯進行了全球性的旅程，促進各地對於[[維納斯計劃|維納斯計劃]]的興趣。<ref>{{Cite video | title = Face of the Future | medium = Digital Video | publisher = [[Television_New_Zealand|TV New Zealand]] | date = 2010 | url = http://tvnz.co.nz/close-up/there-future-money-irrelevant-3464715/video?vid=3464708 | accessdate = March 23, 2011 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192107/http://tvnz.co.nz/close-up/there-future-money-irrelevant-3464715/video?vid=3464708 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.thevenusproject.com/world-tour-lecture-dates/ World Tour Lecture Dates] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906150123/http://www.thevenusproject.com/world-tour-lecture-dates |date=2011-09-06 }}</ref>西元2011年1月15日，《[[時代精神：邁步向前|時代精神：邁步向前]]》({{link-en||Zeitgeist: Moving Forward}}) 公開上映並特別描述了法斯科本人。<ref name="Zeitgeist: Moving Forward">Joseph P. (2011). {{YouTube|4Z9WVZddH9w|"Zeitgeist: Moving Forward"}}</ref>

